Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.54,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.26,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:22.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:34.42,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll smoke it. I can smoke too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Inhale then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Now you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smoke. It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you staying just as you are... until the end of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,19. The Utakata Game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hurry we can make the afternoon classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rei having that girl with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it could happen, since both of them are Seiran students...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...I bet both of them had morning classes, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We skipped classes in high school too, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the last time you saw Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the last time you saw Orihara Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreamtime ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! It's too late in the day for a "good morning"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We called your house over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You called my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Mom said she'd be out today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What could possibly have happened to you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way to school I started feeling ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I took a long rest at the coffee shop near the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So... how do you feel, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now. Sorry to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So at last, I finally said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That dreamlike moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...that one moment alone with her it is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to afternoon classes... then they were over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I would become myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The dreamtime isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, it is expanding, inflating like a giant bubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...getting bigger and bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning Saint-Juste-sama was just sitting there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako! Nanako, for goodness sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last stop! The last stop! We're at the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,These familiar stores, and even the city itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...have somehow taken on a new look today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent your 3000 Yen on that? What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I want to cherish and care for my special "bubble"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...my big, inflated bubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...and hope it doesn't burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where is it? That cafe where you rested this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know! The one you were at while you felt sick this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen it I'm sure... "Cafe la Moulin".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cafe la Moulin? That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try one more... It looks so pretty on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know... Cafe la Moulin doesn't open until afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Today your face says "I'm happy!" and I really like it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stay a little longer with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly I don't want to be alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Rei doing in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she attending classes? Everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... I don't see much of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...because she and I are in different grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the park, in the morning, during classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always acting as if you couldn't care less about her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei "kidnapped" a freshman today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Misonoo Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, barely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We inducted her into the Sorority this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she close to Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Rei doesn't corrupt her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, how did you become acquainted with this freshman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to be alone, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've ever said those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard myself thinking those words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I never thought I would say them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...not aloud, not face-to-face, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't bear being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late today, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you go upstairs... would you come to the living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, only one moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father's done it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I guess I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered if it was a bit too young...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in a display window at a store near the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure it would look good on you, so I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It might make a good party dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma cherie La Poupee... She looks just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what would be in store for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I finally was able to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See, now it's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How was I able to speak to her like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How on earth does she feel about me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, keep it down in the gallery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a regular season game. It's just a scrimmage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all welcome to watch quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we can do without all the screaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a picture of you and Saint-Juste-sama together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe later after the game, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I don't know about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to get you to practice with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...but can't you do something about your "groupies"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should spray them with insecticide?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten really cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it just doesn't mean much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm counting on you to start the next game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean the end of Seiran basketball, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it foolish to speak up like that to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even say "hello" like I used to, anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And while I'm thinking all this, what is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she one of your groupies, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That one... watching you from behind the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, nevermind then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an acquaintance of Henmi Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran into him and my brother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi was still the same old Henmi Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten him. Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to translate literally up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The important part begins at line 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So... let's see... Miss Misonoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Nanako! Your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you translate from line 18, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the literal meaning, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Express the text using your own feeling for the meanings within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ai no Hyohaku-sha...{\i0} Wanderer of Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Koi no"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the context, {\i1}"Koi"{\i0} would be better here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And try {\i1}"sasuraibito"{\i0} instead of {\i1}"hyohaku-sha"{\i0} for "wanderer".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A wanderer of love, I hear the whistle through the evening glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The last train leaving the city has just departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I am not on that train. Once again, I am not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, I can't bear to face the depth of my own heartbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dusk is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dusk is approaching. Once again, I wait, dreading the coming solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I sit alone on these tracks, tracks reddened with rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Far in the distance... do I hear another whistle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hear it? Or just imagine it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Easy, easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a window seat, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're close to the ocean, so there are lots of seagulls flying about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like seagulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seiran cafeteria's fried chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...is actually fried seagull?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the hamburgers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything I say that doesn't make you laugh, seems to make you cry instead....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm strange. I'm not myself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't all that strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling in love makes all of us feel a bit strange, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you something. So I invited you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is Rei you've fallen in love with, you're going to be hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Rei's soul is enslaved to a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They say "to love is to suffer"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's all right if you're the only one hurt by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, one avoids hurting the other, if possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's love, then I'd like to fall in love, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can forget, because I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can forget, because I've loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And even... I'll even forget that I've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved you that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost asked "Did you hurt the one you love?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...but then I saw that she had loved so very deeply,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...her love was so profound,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...that it was beyond my ability to even imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that even now she might still feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is {\i1}"utakata". "Utakata" no koi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Utakata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}utakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is just like a bubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It pops to the surface, lingers for an instant, and is soon gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Life's fleeting instant is like a bubble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all of us in that brief bubble seek to love and be loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Its beauty lies in its brevity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must never despise it for being merely ephemeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we should look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about... the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You were 10, and I was 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in our back yard. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...the only one to see me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only one, my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you must look only at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand? You must never look at anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I have kept these words to myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Should this have remained my secret forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but I... was helpless to hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.92,0:25:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi invites Nanako to attend a university fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.00,0:25:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Nanako is thrilled to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Fukiko becomes upset upon hearing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.56,0:25:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of the university fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.43,0:25:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Fukiko calls Nanako to the Sorority house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.03,0:25:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.81,0:25:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Gardening Shears
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.37,0:25:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
